the primary NLS fact sheet Books for Blind and Physically
Handicapped Individuals.
   A technical circular titled Braille Preservation and
Salvage Guidelines (03-01) is available in regular print and
online at www.loc.gov/nls/technical/circulars/
braillepreservationguidelines.html.

