RC 53998.
##

The Thirty Years' War.
RC 54101.
edited by Geoffrey Parker.
read by Robert Blumenfeld.
3 cassettes.
Essay collection recounting the European conflicts that
became known as the Thirty Years' War (1618-1648) between
