beings led to the Ten Commandments. Posits that the Bible is
also a law book. 2000.
RC 54155.
##

Still Woman Enough: A Memoir.
RC 54166.
by Loretta Lynn.
read by Madelyn Buzzard.
2 cassettes.
Country singer continues her autobiography begun in _Coal
Miner's Daughter (RC 47599)_. Includes reminiscences of her
career and friendship with Conway Twitty, Tammy Wynette, and
other entertainers; her stormy marriage to her late husband,
Doolittle Lynn; and her relationships with her children.
