Slander: Liberal Lies about the American Right.
RC 54437.
by Ann Coulter.
read by Kerry Cundiff.
2 cassettes.
Conservative commentator and author of _High Crimes and
Misdemeanors (RC 47084)_ argues that liberals control the
mainstream media and use it to demonize conservatives and
conservative values. Coulter identifies a "liberal
